  xLinkActuate: 'xlinkActuate',
  xLinkArcRole: 'xlinkArcrole',
  xLinkHref: 'xlinkHref',
  xLinkRole: 'xlinkRole',

/**

 */
export const hastToReact = {

  itemId: 'itemID',
  strokeDashArray: 'strokeDasharray',
  strokeDashOffset: 'strokeDashoffset',
